]}]},{id:\"atg-basics\",name:\"ATG \\xb7 KNEES OVER TOES\",time:15,focus:\"mobility\",intensity:\"low\",source:\"Knees Over Toes Guy (Ben Patrick)\",description:\"Tibialis raises \\xb7 ATG split squat \\xb7 sled drag. Bulletproof knees.\",scienceNote:\"Loaded end-range knee flexion strengthens VMO and patellar tendon at angles where most lifters are weakest. Reduces patellofemoral pain.\",citation:\"Patrick (2022) ATG for Life\",exercises:[{name:\"Tibialis Raise\",setsReps:\"3 \\xd7 25 \\xb7 against wall\",cue:\"Toes pull up. Heels stay planted.\",videoQuery:\"tibialis raise atg knees over toes\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]},{name:\"ATG Split Squat\",setsReps:\"3 \\xd7 10/leg\",cue:\"Front knee tracks past toe. No pain.\",videoQuery:\"atg split squat knees over toes\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]},{name:\"Reverse Sled Drag\",setsReps:\"3 \\xd7 30m \\xb7 light\",cue:\"Walk backwards. Quads on fire.\",videoQuery:\"reverse sled drag atg\",equipment:[\"sled\"],alternatives:[{name:\"Banded Backward Walk\",equipment:[\"bands\"],videoQuery:\"band backward walk knee health\"}]}]},{id:\"hip-flexor-reclaim\",name:\"HIP FLEXOR RECLAIM\",time:12,focus:\"mobility\",intensity:\"low\",description:\"Couch stretch \\xb7 90/90 \\xb7 half-kneeling lunge. Reverse desk-life damage.\",scienceNote:\"Sitting >6 hr/day shortens iliopsoas and rectus femoris, anteriorly tilting pelvis and inhibiting glute activation. Daily reset is non-negotiable past 30.\",citation:\"Sahrmann (2002) Diagnosis and Treatment of Movement Impairment Syndromes\",exercises:[{name:\"Couch Stretch\",setsReps:\"2 \\xd7 60s/leg\",cue:\"Squeeze glute on stretching side.\",videoQuery:\"couch stretch hip flexor squat university\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]},{name:\"90/90 Hip Switch\",setsReps:\"10 switches\",cue:\"Sit tall. Both knees pin to ground.\",videoQuery:\"90 90 hip mobility squat university\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]},{name:\"Half-Kneeling Lunge Stretch\",setsReps:\"2 \\xd7 45s/leg\",videoQuery:\"half kneeling lunge stretch squat university\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]}]},{id:\"shoulder-prehab\",name:\"SHOULDER PREHAB FLOW\",time:10,focus:\"mobility\",intensity:\"low\",description:\"Band pull-aparts \\xb7 dislocates \\xb7 scap pulls. Pre-workout staple.\",scienceNote:\"External rotators are 30% weaker than internal rotators in untrained lifters. Pre-fatigue daily to prevent impingement.\",citation:\"Cools et al. (2007) Br J Sports Med 41(11):874\",exercises:[{name:\"Band Pull-Apart\",setsReps:\"3 \\xd7 20\",cue:\"Squeeze shoulder blades.\",videoQuery:\"band pull apart shoulder squat university\",equipment:[\"bands\"]},{name:\"Band Shoulder Dislocate\",setsReps:\"3 \\xd7 10\",cue:\"Pass band overhead with straight arms.\",videoQuery:\"band shoulder dislocate squat university\",equipment:[\"bands\"]},{name:\"Scapular Pull-up\",setsReps:\"3 \\xd7 10\",cue:\"Hang. Shoulder blades down only.\",videoQuery:\"scapular pull up form squat university\",equipment:[\"pullup\"],alternatives:[{name:\"Wall Slide\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"],videoQuery:\"wall slide scap mobility\"}]}]},{id:\"tspine-opener\",name:\"T-SPINE OPENERS\",time:8,focus:\"mobility\",intensity:\"low\",description:\"Cat-cow \\xb7 foam-roll t-spine \\xb7 thread the needle. Restore overhead position.\",scienceNote:\"Thoracic rotation drives overhead reach, hip rotation, and rib-cage breathing. Restricted t-spine limits squat depth and OHP lockout.\",citation:\"Cook (2010) Movement\",exercises:[{name:\"Cat-Cow\",setsReps:\"10 reps slow\",videoQuery:\"cat cow stretch form\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]},{name:\"Foam Roll T-Spine\",setsReps:\"60s \\xb7 3 spots\",cue:\"Pause and exhale on tight spots.\",videoQuery:\"foam roll thoracic spine squat university\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]},{name:\"Thread the Needle\",setsReps:\"8/side\",videoQuery:\"thread the needle stretch\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]}]},{id:\"478-breath\",name:\"4-7-8 BREATH PROTOCOL\",time:8,focus:\"recovery\",intensity:\"low\",source:\"Andrew Weil \\xb7 Ben Greenfield\",description:\"Inhale 4s \\xb7 hold 7s \\xb7 exhale 8s. Sleep onset, anxiety dampening, vagal tone.\",scienceNote:\"Slow exhale-dominant breathing (5\\u20136 breaths/min) maximises HRV and vagal activation. Reduces cortisol and improves sleep onset by ~15 min.\",citation:\"Russo et al. (2017) Breathe 13(4):298\",exercises:[{name:\"4-7-8 Breath\",setsReps:\"8 min \\xb7 4 in / 7 hold / 8 out \\xb7 nasal only\",cue:\"Tongue behind upper teeth. Exhale through pursed lips with audible whoosh.\",videoQuery:\"4 7 8 breathing technique andrew weil ben greenfield\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]}]},{id:\"greenfield-stack\",name:\"GREENFIELD HEAT+COLD STACK\",time:25,focus:\"recovery\",intensity:\"med\",source:\"Ben Greenfield\",description:\"15 min sauna (80\\u201390\\xb0C) \\u2192 2 min cold plunge \\u2192 5 min Z2 walk. Hormetic stack.\",scienceNote:\"Heat-shock proteins (HSP70/72) up 50% post-sauna; cold raises norepinephrine ~530%. Pairing produces broader stress-resilience adaptations than either alone.\",citation:\"Laukkanen et al. (2018) Mayo Clin Proc 93(8):1111\",exercises:[{name:\"Sauna\",setsReps:\"15 min \\xb7 80\\u201390\\xb0C\",cue:\"Stay until uncomfortable, not unsafe. Hydrate after.\",videoQuery:\"sauna protocol benefits ben greenfield\",equipment:[\"sauna\"],alternatives:[{name:\"Hot Bath (40\\xb0C)\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"],videoQuery:\"hot bath heat shock protocol\"}]},{name:\"Cold Plunge\",setsReps:\"2 min \\xb7 5\\u201310\\xb0C\",cue:\"Slow exhale. Stay still. Don't fight the urge.\",videoQuery:\"cold plunge protocol ben greenfield\",equipment:[\"ice\"],alternatives:[{name:\"Cold Shower\",equipment:[\"ice\"],videoQuery:\"cold shower protocol benefits\"}]},{name:\"Z2 Walk\",setsReps:\"5 min \\xb7 easy pace\",cue:\"Cool down. Re-establish parasympathetic.\",videoQuery:\"post recovery walk\",equipment:[\"bodyweight\"]}]},{id:\"para-reset\",name:\"PARASYMPATHETIC RESET\",time:10,focus:\"recovery\",intensity:\"low\",description:\"Box breathing 4-